Source: pakiti
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Daniel Kouril <kouril@ics.muni.cz>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), perl
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://github.com/CESNET/pakiti3
#Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/collab-maint/pakiti.git

Package: pakiti-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, curl, openssl, perl
Description: Patch Status Monitoring Tool
 Pakiti provides a monitoring mechanism to check the patching status of
 Linux systems.
 .
 This package provides the client part that is able to send information
 about installed software to a defined Pakiti server.

Package: pakiti-server
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, curl, apache2, mysql-server, php5, libapache2-mod-php5, php5-mysql, php5-curl, subversion
Description: Patch Status Monitoring Tool
 Pakiti provides a monitoring mechanism to check the patching status of
 Linux systems.
 .
 This package provides the server part that is able to send information
 about installed software to a defined Pakiti server.

